  <PropertyGroup>
    <Guid>f49e19ab-7264-4ac3-b334-1ed8b9151580</Guid>
    <Name>Avatar Project Influences Difficulty</Name>
    <Description>By default, XCOM 2 has the vast majority of its missions function like they did in EU, increasing in difficulty as time passes.

The only exception to this are the alien facility missions, which instead uses the Avatar Project's progress to derive its difficulty from.

This mod makes it so all missions now use that form of difficulty calculation.</Description>
    <SteamPublishID>0</SteamPublishID>
    <AssemblyName>Doom-based Mission Difficulty</AssemblyName>
    <RootNamespace>Doom-based Mission Difficulty</RootNamespace>
  </PropertyGroup>
